minijava.typecheck.symboltable
类 GlobalTable

java.lang.Object
  minijava.typecheck.symboltable.SymbolTable
      minijava.typecheck.symboltable.GlobalTable

public class GlobalTable
extends SymbolTable

Identified by main class name. Usage: Insert and find all classes.
Used via "(any instance of SymbolTable).globalTable" (Recommended)

作者：
ZongZiWang

checkInheritanceLoop

public boolean checkInheritanceLoop()
Check if there is inheritance loop during the source file.
If there is, the Compiler should be shut down right now.

返回：
true => there is
false => there is not

false => there is not

true => there is
false => there is not

checkUnusedVariables

public boolean checkUnusedVariables()
Check if there is unused variables during the source file.
It works when "EnableWarning" of TypeCheckVisitor is true

返回：
true => there is
false => there is not

isTypeMatch

public boolean isTypeMatch(TypeTable type,
                           TypeTable param)
Check if the type of "param" matches the type of "type"

参数：
type -
param -
返回：
true => if the types are same or the type of "type" is the ancestor of the type of "param"
false => does not match
